text: kraoyomk nowpel del a l laoh ban bratan aoy puok keat teangpir nouv kaun da la mneak puokkeat teangpir kaban thveu shi ri k champoh a l laoh( knong kar dakchhmoh kaun) nouv avei del trong ban bratan aoy puokke teangpir nih towvinh . haey a l laoh khpangkhpasa ampi avei del puokke kampoung thveu shi ri k noh
